<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Within the wikification the top and bottom links can only jump to the next and the previous chapter.</p>

<p>It would be better if the links could also jump to the next section.</p>

<p>Example:
Chapter a
  Section 1
  Section 1
    Section 2
    Section 2
Chapter b</p>

<p>Not you can only jump from a to b
Better would be if you could jump : a1 -&gt; 1 -&gt; b.
Jumps should always jump from one page to the next page of the documentation not the next chapter.</p>

